headline: Cisco Research: Innovation Funding Gap Revealed in Canadian Businesses
summary: Nearly all Canadians believe innovation is essential to our future prosperity — and expect businesses to lead the way. Cisco, the global leader in networking and security, revealed new research that shows 93% of business leaders and 89% of Canadians agree that the future of innovation in this country rests with business, not government.
